External libraries: 
    I've decided to include well known 3p dependencies to avoid spending time on well known functionality that is not part of the task.
    
    - Underscore.js
        Reason: Provides set of utility functions
    - Require.js
        Reason: Provides handy mechanism to manage dependencies and define modules in a separate files.

Test in browser: Chrome 44.0.2403.130 (64-bit)
